{"pv20:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv20:0.2":"Ubbarivagga ","pv20:0.3":"8. Culasetthipetavatthu ","pv20:1.1":"“Naggo kiso pabbajitosi bhante, ","pv20:1.2":"Rattim kuhim gacchasi kissa hetu; ","pv20:1.3":"Acikkha me tam api sakkunemu, ","pv20:1.4":"Sabbena vittam patipadaye tuvan”ti. ","pv20:2.1":"“Baranasi nagaram duraghuttham, ","pv20:2.2":"Tatthaham gahapati addhako ahu dino; ","pv20:2.3":"Adata gedhitamano amisasmim, ","pv20:2.4":"Dussilyena yamavisayamhi patto. ","pv20:3.1":"So sucikaya kilamito tehi, ","pv20:3.2":"Teneva natisu yami amisakincikkhahetu; ","pv20:3.3":"Adanasila na ca saddahanti, ","pv20:3.4":"Danaphalam hoti paramhi loke. ","pv20:4.1":"Dhita ca mayham lapate abhikkhanam, ","pv20:4.2":"‘Dassami danam pitunam pitamahanam’; ","pv20:4.3":"Tamupakkhatam parivisayanti brahmana, ","pv20:4.4":"‘Yami aham andhakavindam bhottun’”ti. ","pv20:5.1":"Tamavoca raja “anubhaviyana tampi, ","pv20:5.2":"Eyyasi khippam ahamapi kassam pujam; ","pv20:5.3":"Acikkha me tam yadi atthi hetu, ","pv20:5.4":"Saddhayitam hetuvaco sunoma”ti. ","pv20:6.1":"“Tatha”ti vatva agamasi tattha, ","pv20:6.2":"Bhunjimsu bhattam na ca dakkhinaraha; ","pv20:6.3":"Paccagami rajagaham punaparam, ","pv20:6.4":"Paturahosi purato janadhipassa. ","pv20:7.1":"Disvana petam punadeva agatam, ","pv20:7.2":"Raja avoca “ahamapi kim dadami; ","pv20:7.3":"Acikkha me tam yadi atthi hetu, ","pv20:7.4":"Yena tuvam cirataram pinito siya”ti. ","pv20:8.1":"“Buddhanca sangham parivisiyana raja, ","pv20:8.2":"Annena panena ca civarena; ","pv20:8.3":"Tam dakkhinam adisa me hitaya, ","pv20:8.4":"Evam aham cirataram pinito siya”ti. ","pv20:9.1":"Tato ca raja nipatitva tavade, ","pv20:9.2":"Danam sahattha atulam daditva sanghe; ","pv20:9.3":"Arocesi pakatam tathagatassa, ","pv20:9.4":"Tassa ca petassa dakkhinam adisittha. ","pv20:10.1":"So pujito ativiya sobhamano, ","pv20:10.2":"Paturahosi purato janadhipassa; ","pv20:10.3":"“Yakkhohamasmi paramiddhipatto, ","pv20:10.4":"Na mayhamatthi sama sadisa manusa. ","pv20:11.1":"Passanubhavam aparimitam mamayidam, ","pv20:11.2":"Tayanudittham atulam datva sanghe; ","pv20:11.3":"Santappito satatam sada bahuhi, ","pv20:11.4":"Yami aham sukhito manussadeva”ti. ","pv20:12.1":"Culasetthipetavatthu atthamam. ","pv20:12.2":"Bhanavaram pathamam. "}